Example of a multi-tenant app using devise and can-can.

Run bundle install.

Run rake db:migrate

Example at http://multi-tenant-devise.heroku.com/users/sign_in. Click the 'Sign up' link to create you own admin user
and organization. You can then create other users associated with your organization.

See also http://lumbee-on-rails.blogspot.com/2011/11/multi-tenant-rails-app.html